About Us
We are a family-owned business established in 2002 by Cristi and Patrick Purpura and one of the oldest eateries in Seminole Heights. Located in an 1898 Victorian House we have inside dining, and outside seating on the porch. Downstairs you will find Bart's Tavern where we feature live music every weekend. Our recipes are made fresh from scratch using the best ingredients. Our mission is to be your favorite locally-owned watering hole, a place where friends can gather to celebrate great food, great libations and great times.
Pet friendly outside.
Our recipes are made fresh from scratch using the best ingredients we can find.  Our mission is to be your favorite locally-owned watering hole, a place where friends can gather to celebrate great food, great libations and great times.
Well behaved dogs are allowed outside on the porch and downstairs at Bart's Tavern.
